WEBVTT

00:08:58.221 --> 00:09:00.122
We just wait for the rain to go.

00:09:00.122 --> 00:09:03.716
We take the sand, we mix it with clay,

00:09:03.716 --> 00:09:06.502
and we keep building.

00:09:06.502 --> 00:09:08.307
That is it.

00:09:08.307 --> 00:09:11.401
The Gando project was always
connected to training the people,

00:09:11.401 --> 00:09:14.893
because I just wanted, one day

00:09:14.893 --> 00:09:17.796
when I fall down and die,

00:09:17.796 --> 00:09:20.480
that at least one person from Gando

00:09:20.480 --> 00:09:24.222
keeps doing this work.

00:09:24.222 --> 00:09:27.065
But you will be surprised. I'm still alive.

00:09:27.065 --> 00:09:28.615
(Laughter)

00:09:28.615 --> 00:09:31.792
And my people now can use their skills